title: About Time
overview: At the age of 21, Tim discovers he can travel in time and change what happens and has happened in his own life. His decision to make his world a better place by getting a girlfriend turns out not to be as easy as you might think.

title: Harvey
overview: Due to his insistence that he has an invisible six foot-tall rabbit for a best friend, a whimsical middle-aged man is thought by his family to be insane - but he may be wiser than anyone knows.

title: Being John Malkovich
overview: A puppeteer discovers a portal that leads literally into the head of movie star John Malkovich.

title: Good Bye Lenin!
overview: In 1990, to protect his fragile mother from a fatal shock after a long coma, a young man must keep her from learning that her beloved nation of East Germany as she knew it has disappeared.

title: Vizontele
overview: Lives of residents in a small Anatolian village change when television is introduced to them

title: Kimi no na wa.
overview: Two strangers find themselves linked in a bizarre way. When a connection forms, will distance be the only thing to keep them apart?

title: Death Note: Desu nôto
overview: A battle between the world's two greatest minds begins when Light Yagami finds the Death Note, a notebook with the power to kill, and decides to rid the world of criminals.

title: Adaptation.
overview: A lovelorn screenwriter becomes desperate as he tries and fails to adapt 'The Orchid Thief' by Susan Orlean for the screen.

title: Sabrina
overview: A playboy becomes interested in the daughter of his family's chauffeur, but it's his more serious brother who would be the better man for her.

title: His Girl Friday
overview: A newspaper editor uses every trick in the book to keep his ace reporter ex-wife from remarrying.

title: Chhichhore
overview: A tragic incident forces Anirudh, a middle-aged man, to take a trip down memory lane and reminisce his college days along with his friends, who were labelled as losers.

title: Manhattan
overview: The life of a divorced television writer dating a teenage girl is further complicated when he falls in love with his best friend's mistress.

title: Badhaai ho
overview: A man is embarrassed when he finds out his mother is pregnant.

title: Druk
overview: Four friends, all high school teachers, test a theory that they will improve their lives by maintaining a constant level of alcohol in their blood.

title: Captain Fantastic
overview: In the forests of the Pacific Northwest, a father devoted to raising his six kids with a rigorous physical and intellectual education is forced to leave his paradise and enter the world, challenging his idea of what it means to be a parent.

title: Dead Man
overview: On the run after murdering a man, accountant William Blake encounters a strange aboriginal American man named Nobody who prepares him for his journey into the spiritual world.

title: Jojo Rabbit
overview: A young boy in Hitler's army finds out his mother is hiding a Jewish girl in their home.

title: La règle du jeu
overview: A bourgeois life in France at the onset of World War II, as the rich and their poor servants meet up at a French chateau.

title: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara
overview: Three friends decide to turn their fantasy vacation into reality after one of their friends gets engaged.

title: Little Miss Sunshine
overview: A family determined to get their young daughter into the finals of a beauty pageant take a cross-country trip in their VW bus.
